TextEng: Goodbye for now.
What is your job? Do you fight?
I will fight for my first medal.
I'm ready to try for the next medal round.
Text: 다음 회전 메달에 도전할 준비가 됐습니다.

TextEng: Me fight for first medal!
What you do? You fight?
Me leave for now, okay?
What are the rules?
What rules is for fight?
Me ready to try for next medal up thing!
Text: 나 다음 메달 거 도전 준비 됐어!

TextEng: Why is he unbeatable?
Why he so tough?
You will keep the battle fair, won't you?
Text: 이번 싸움 공정하게 진행해 주실 거죠?

TextEng: You keeps it fair though, right?
Bring him on!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> It should be fair. You know that.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You should make it fair. That only right.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 공정하게 해야 해. 그게 맞는 거야.

TextEng: Do we let him give humans a bad name?
Text: 인간의 평판을 더럽히게 그냥 둘 겁니까?

TextEng: We not let hims give humans shame.
Text: 우린 그놈이 인간 망신 시키게 안 둬.

TextEng: I can pay you. 400 gold will get you away.
Text: 돈을 드리죠. 금화 400이면 자리를 비켜 주시겠습니까?

TextEng: Me pay you 400 gold so you free to leave.
Text: 나 금화 400 줄게. 그럼 너 떠나도 돼.

TextEng: You've already been paid to keep it fair.
You already paid to make fair fight.
He is still giving humans a bad name.
Text: 그는 여전히 인간의 평판을 더럽히고 있어요.

TextEng: He still shame humans.
Me needs healing, okay?
I ask that you heal me.
